videos.description: Eastern Michigan QB Brogan Roback connects with Sergio Bailey II for a 20-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Eastern Michigan cashes in on Kentucky turnover

videos.description: Kentucky QB Stephen Johnson hooks up with Greg Hart for the 20-yard touchdown, tying the score.
videos.headline: Kentucky answers back with 20-yard TD

videos.description: Kentucky's Charles Walker catches the 12-yard pass and absorbs the big hit from Juan Giraldo, who is ejected for targeting.
videos.headline: Eastern Michigan safety lowers boom, ejected for targeting

videos.description: Kentucky QB Stephen Johnson throws his second touchdown pass to Tavin Richardson for a seven-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Richardson's TD gives Kentucky first lead of game

videos.description: Eastern Michigan QB Brogan Roback laterals the ball to Jaron Johnson who hits John Niupalau for the 43-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Eastern Michigan pulls off trick play to tie game

videos.description: Kentucky head coach Mark Stoops talks about the two big plays which have hurt them and what he thinks of his team's offensive effort.
videos.headline: Stoops: 'We have to be more consistent'

videos.description: Eastern Michigan returner Eddie Daugherty fumbles the punt return and it is recovered by Kentucky's Tristan Yeomans.
videos.headline: Botched punt return gives Kentucky the ball back

videos.description: Kentucky's Joshua Paschal blocks the punt from Jake Julien and gives Kentucky the ball back at the Eastern Michigan 12-yard line.
videos.headline: Blocked punt puts Kentucky in red zone

videos.description: Kentucky RB Benny Snell Jr. gets the handoff and breaks tackles for a 12-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Kentucky cashes in on turnover, pads lead

videos.description: Eastern Michigan QB Brogan Roback's pass is intercepted by Kendall Randolph and returns it to the Kentucky 10-yard line.
videos.headline: Eastern Michigan interception halts drive

videos.description: Ian Eriksen runs right and into the end zone for the two-yard touchdown late in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Late TD pulls Eastern Michigan within four of Kentucky

videos.description: Kentucky head coach Mark Stoops breaks down how big the blocked punt was and what his team needs to do going forward.
videos.headline: Stoops: 'We had some really good stops'

videos.description: The Wildcats create three turnovers and limit the Eagles to 13 rushing yards in their win.
videos.headline: Kentucky defeats Eastern Michigan 24-20
